{"tid":1698400,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說「推」 試著說「1111三大罷」","createTime":"2019-11-07T12:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T04:24:47.000Z","uid":309825,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8746be08bfd7d532a20f27f45bb80f6996ebcf2d","tid":1698400,"uid":309825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:43:12.000Z","msg":"不要推廢po 想討論其他嘢就用不推文回覆<br />\n推文時說「<span style=\"color: gold;\">1111三大罷</span>」<br />\n<br />\n越嚟越多 分化po 查案po 打飛機ok<br />\n見到呢啲po 直頭唔好㩒入去<br />\n大家一齊推同討論11月11日嘅三大罷<br />\n推到同85個氣氛一樣咁勁<br />\n<br />\n黑警越做越過份 文宣趁住呢一兩日<br />\nAirDrop 派傳單 <br />\n再加埋十點咆哮加多句 1111三大罷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要全世界都知 成唔成功一件事<br />\n唔要罷完都冇人知要罷</span></span></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"5b3ce5434f9223552d23eb015e9d56c02770fded","tid":1698400,"uid":309825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:44:04.000Z","msg":"1111三大罷"},{"pid":"2351e1fb045ff9dbdf851f108c95f28100eb354a","tid":1698400,"uid":309825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:44:26.000Z","msg":"1111三大罷"},{"pid":"5a9022096eefa237247a04597c277e27164a7976","tid":1698400,"uid":309825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:44:37.000Z","msg":"1111三大罷"},{"pid":"95605767024faa934f628556df9b4424a6b603ee","tid":1698400,"uid":309825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:44:48.000Z","msg":"1111三大罷"},{"pid":"61125e2e3f79884ca97902c45b206cffe898178f","tid":1698400,"uid":309825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:45:05.000Z","msg":"1111三大罷"},{"pid":"d86a044acf1d9b29b236719786d6c2494916b615","tid":1698400,"uid":309825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:45:15.000Z","msg":"1111三大罷"},{"pid":"41771fc275e41c5b2d03c39f8014c31e1fe92b42","tid":1698400,"uid":309825,"like":0,"dislik